+ <dani-garcia@users.noreply.github.com>
+Date: Tue, 23 Jun 2026 17:45:38 +0200
+Subject: [PATCH] [PM-34331] Update electron to 41 (#20448)
+
+* [PM-34331] Update electron to 41
+
+* Update beta version too
+
+* Enable new fuse
+
+* Fix process-reload bug
+
+* Update electron to fix node 24 bug
+
+---------
+
+Co-authored-by: kmancusi0105 <kmancusi@bitwarden.com>
